ntibody_therapeutics.aspx',NULL,'PharmaTimes',NULL,'산업동향',NULL,NULL,1,0,NULL,'제약/바이오','U151225I05',NULL,'2015-12-08'),(2993,'A SKIN PATCH OF IBUPROFEN APPLIES MEDICATION DIRECTLY TO PAIN','영국 워윅대, ‘이부프로펜’ 패치제 개발',NULL,1449500400,0,1572589149,'http://www.popsci.com/scientists-create-first-patch-for-ibuprofen',NULL,'Popular Science',NULL,'산업동향',NULL,NULL,1,7,NULL,'의료기기/정보화','U151225I06',NULL,'2015-12-08'),(2994,'Roche buys into SQZ engineering tech in $500m deal','로슈, 5억불에 세포치료 분야 \'SQZ 기술\' 확보',NULL,1449500400,0,1572589149,'http://www.pharmatimes.com/Article/15-12-08/Roche_buys_into_SQZ_engineering_tech_in_500m_deal.aspx',NULL,'Pharma Times',NULL,'산업동향',NULL,NULL,1,0,NULL,'제약/바이오','U151225I07',NULL,'2015-12-08'),(2995,'Swine flu outbreak nears Tehran as Iran death toll tops 40','이란, 신종플루로 40명 이상 사망',NULL,1449673200,0,1572589149,'http://tribune.com.pk/story/1007634/swine-flu-outbreak-nears-tehran-as-iran-death-toll-tops-40/',NULL,' Express Tribune',NULL,'정책동향',NULL,NULL,1,2,NULL,'보건산업 기타','U151225P08',NULL,'2015-12-10'),(2996,'FDA APPROVES GUNSHOT-STAUNCHING XSTAT INVENTION FOR CIVILIAN USE','FDA, 상처구멍 막는 지혈 드레싱 승인',NULL,1449586800,0,1572589149,'http://www.popsci.com/fda-approves-gunshot-staunching-invention-for-use-in-civilian-population',NULL,'Popular Science',NULL,'정책동향',NULL,NULL,1,0,NULL,'의료기기/정보화','U151225P09',NULL,'2015-12-09'),(2997,'FDA panel recommends approval of Teva\'s biotech asthma drug\n','FDA, 테바 천식 항체 치료제 승인 ',NULL,1449586800,0,1572589149,'http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/international/business/fda-panel-recommends-approval-of-tevas-biotech-asthma-drug/articleshow/50126717.cms',NULL,'Economic Times',NULL,'정책동향',NULL,NULL,1,2,NULL,'제약/바이오','U151225P10',NULL,'2015-12-09'),(2998,'FDA Gives Palbociclib Priority Review for Pretreated HR-Positive/HER2-Negative Breast Cancer','FDA, 화이자 ‘이브란스’ 적응증 추가 신속심사',NULL,1449673200,0,1572589149,'http://www.targetedonc.com/news/fda-palbociclib-priority-review-pretreated-hr-positive-her2-breast-cancer',NULL,'Tar